| Backup Object                              | Example                                               | Impact | Reason                                           |
| ------------------------------------------ | ----------------------------------------------------- | ------ | ------------------------------------------------ |
| Databases (SQL / Oracle)                   | Database full backups or log backups under Legal Hold | Medium | Retained beyond policy, increasing storage usage |
